pan class="style4">はず</span>です。(Yamada-san is supposed          to eat sushi tonight.) <br>          Compare: 私は今晩すしを食べる<span class="style5">つもり</span>です。(My intention: <span class="style5">I          plan</span> to eat sushi tonight.)      <br>      </p>      </td>  </tr>  <tr>    <td height="46" colspan="4"><p>私は薬を飲んだから、もうよくなる<span class="style4">はず</span>だ。(Since        I took medicine, I ought to get well soon.) </p>      </td>    </tr></table><br><br><ul>    <li><B>練習 (Practice Quizzes)</B>      <ul>        <li><a href="../../../gquiz/y2/412l/gq_y2_412l_hazu.php">Quiz: 〜はず</a></li>      </ul>    </li>    <blockquote>          <p>&nbsp;</p>    </blockquote>     			<p align="center"><a href="#top">Return to Top</a> </p> 			<p align="center"><a href="../../../../glist.php">Ｒeturn to Grammar Lists</a></p>	  </UL>          </tr></table></BODY></HTML>